ike":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T10:52:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">尋找黑警性暴力證人/受害者，協助國際遊說</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2640629789347426&amp;id=124616407615456\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2640629789347426%26id%3D124616407615456&d=2Jo0d4zpMW7MEYOmRW2Ldfno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=b98849ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2640629789347426&amp;id=124616407615456</a><br />\n<br />\nPost：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eDEkrT\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eDEkrT</a><br />\n<br />\n//平等機會婦女聯席發言人區美寶稱，3個組織11月初共同發起控訴警察性暴力的國際聯署，截至本月7日收集到21國共85個團體聯署支持。為了向聯合國專家展開更有力游說，3個組織呼籲受害者主動聯絡他們並接受訪談，強調會保密。//<br />\n<br />\n我們現正收集抗爭者在抗爭期間／被捕後遭受警察性暴力對待的資料，作以下用途：<br />\n1. 協助受害人可以完整保留該事件之紀錄<br />\n2. 整理資料並製成 #ProtestToo 實錄，以作追究之用<br />\n3. 收集國際聯署（進行中），結合個案提交聯合國，爭取國際間關注及支持<br />\n4. 要求香港政府獨立、公正地徹查「反送中運動」發生的性暴力<br />\n<br />\n*個人資料及通訊紀錄在實錄完成後可按受訪者意願全部銷毀<br />\n詳情及相關安排請聯絡Tg @protesttoo"},{"pid":"4cc1f587a8481f2d69b836dca9587c3266ddf93d","tid":1775834,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T10:58:06.000Z","msg":"工黨或成最大贏家，唱返首歌賀一賀佢<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kDIuApfVxBg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkDIuApfVxBg&d=2Jo0d4zpMW7MEYOmRW2Ldfno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=ee072f68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kDIuApfVxBg</a>"},{"pid":"849fba6fb8ae89f2515b48e24fab33f38ea78d0e","tid":1775834,"uid":120587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T23:02:30.000Z","msg":"更重點好似係燈 Second Referendum wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37127fdf3617e2cec9f54f02f88b8054d0603396","tid":1775834,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T05:00:09.000Z","msg":"靜靜地贏唔得嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma